{"tid":2319304,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本遵從美國制裁令 促與美營運的當地銀行凍結林鄭在日戶口","createTime":"2020-12-10T04:13:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T10:05:29.000Z","uid":41343,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"011e7fb873c5c9638013213a254c4486e0c0901e","tid":2319304,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T04:13:21.000Z","msg":"《南華早報》報道，日本政府也遵守美國的制裁指令，要求有與美國營運的日本銀行，凍結林鄭在日本的戶口、或不批准林鄭在日本開設戶口。<br />\n<br />\n日本民主黨眾議員松原仁（Jin Matsubara）指，相信此舉會惹怒中國共產黨，又指今次的制裁安排也涵蓋其他10位8月時被美國制裁的中港官員。<br />\n<br />\n#港版國安法<br />\n【日本遵從美國制裁令 促與美營運的當地銀行凍結林鄭在日戶口】<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3gyvLNB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3gyvLNB&d=DJHqE1tJ5F0S1%2BmpD1KYppugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=868b9467\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3gyvLNB</a>"},{"pid":"0be357b28d61609fb1a432a6da88efdecc9b6e5a","tid":2319304,"uid":19557,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T06:25:07.000Z","msg":"哇 真係全部叫民主黨既都係仆街黎架喎"},{"pid":"480213e086cd74162fd221d4f50398d4103072af","tid":2319304,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T06:26:43.000Z","msg":"民主黨 my Japan <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b88700a51ff331e6ae79b09bd8d573662af1ab76","tid":2319304,"uid":30084,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0be357b28d61609fb1a432a6da88efdecc9b6e5a","tid":2319304,"uid":19557,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T06:25:07.000Z","msg":"哇 真係全部叫民主黨既都係仆街黎架喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T06:27:25.000Z","msg":"唔好俾藉口共產黨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ixyWatq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FixyWatq.jpg&h=8c347403&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6af4aef9d53ca3272186fb4f7b94fb3b6a018276","tid":2319304,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T10:05:29